author: Soo Kim
title: Over 100 Doctors and Nurses Have Died Combating Coronavirus Across the World
description: Over half of the doctors and nurses who died after testing positive have been in Italy, where more than 9,000 health workers have been infected so far, nearly the same amount as in Spain.
content: The novel coronavirus has killed over 100 doctors and nurses around the world, nearly half of whom are reported to be in Italy. The U.S. saw its first emergency physician die after showing COVID-19 symptoms this week. Several other healthcare workers have die… [+32402 chars]
